                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable No.</hi> 58.) I saw the prisoner and Cuthbert together, and assisted in securing the prisoner—I saw him drop the cloth from under his arm—he would not give any address.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I found the clothe in Watling-street, placed in a doorway.</p>
